6:
Okay! Today's the day we finally tackle 
a new floor. You guys ready to go?
9:
Word's been going around about 
a dragon of sorts, right?
12:
Yup! Impervious to magic, apparently. 
I wouldn't be able to do much myself, 
but that's what you're all here for!
14:
We're mostly on the offensive today, 
so Stella, you canâ€”
20: Hey... Aren't you one of Ash's lackeys?
23:
Ellya... You've gotta help... They're in 
trouble...
29:
I was in the Kaleidoscope with Ash... 
He wanted to go deeper than you, 
so we kept going...
30:
We... we didn't stand a chance against 
those monsters...
32:
You guys went into the depths alone?! 
What the hell was he thinking?!
34:
Thanks to him, I made it out alive... 
But he's still in there. 
Please... save them...
38: All right, listen up! Change of plans.
41:
I'm going in there to save them... 
Can I count on you guys to help?
44:
Do you even need to ask? 
We're with you all the way.
50:
Alk. Stella. Make sure this guy gets to

59:
Got it! I'll contact the guild and catch 
up with you later.
64:
All right. Light, Nimbus, I'm going in. 
Make sure you guys stick with me!
72:
Just leave me... Save yourself... 
If you stay here, you'll...
74: I can't just leave you here, boss!
80: S-see, look! Help came after all!
82: D-damn... It had to be you, huh, Ellya?
84:
Hmph. You must've made a deal with 
the devil to get this far.
87:
Heh... D-did you come here to laugh 
at me?
89:
It looks like you have enough energy 
to talk smack, at least. 
Can you stand? Let's get you outta here.
91: Here, boss... Lean on my shoulder.
106:
That must be the dragon. 
Ellya, I don't like these odds.
110:
Me neither. Looks like my Dragon 
Slayer title will have to wait for 
another day.
111:
Assuming we make it out of here alive, 
that is.
116:
Nimbus, get Ash and the others out of 
here!
125:
Soul of luster, locked and loaded! 
Luminous Splash!
129:
The rumors were true... 
It IS impervious to magic!
134: Ellya, watch out for its breath!
145: I'm fine, but at this rate...
148:
No. Not like this. I have an idea. 
Snuff out your torches!
150:
How are we going to see the dragon 
ifâ€”
154:
I know, I know! You're just gonna have 
to trust me! Close your eyes 
until I give the signal, okay?
163:
Whatever you're tryin' here... 
It'd better work!
167:
That's right... come at me... 
juuust like that.
179:
Now, everyone! 
Let's make a run for it!
184:
Hang in there, Ellya! 
We've almost made it!
188:
Y-yeah... I know... 
but I used up... all my power back 
there...
197:
I'm sorry, Light. 
Just leave me... 
and get out while you can...
201: You know I can't do thatâ€”
224:
See? 
We can pull our weight when it 
counts!
233:
Once word got out that you went in to 
save Ash, all of them demanded to 
join in and help.
235:
They're all people you've turned down 
in the past, right?
240: Yeah... A whole bunch of familiar faces.
243:
Most of them here to redeem 
themselves before you, no doubt.
245:
I was blown away, to be honest. 
They're all so much more capable 
than I ever thought they were.
248:
I guess I might've been a little too 
quick to judge them, huh?
251:
Hmm... I don't think it was wrong of 
you to turn them down though.
253:
It's a well-known fact that many lose 
their lives every year venturing into 
the Kaleidoscope unprepared.
254:
But that seems to be on the downturn 
with our latest recruits. I'm sure you 
had something to do with that.
260:
Ash said he never wanted to see you 
in a state like that again.
262:
You've become something of a role 
model to the new blood.
265:
So... When's our next shot at the next 
level gonna be? You haven't given up 
yet, have you?
273:
You're talking to the future record 
holder for the fastest Kaleidoscope 
run, and don't you forget it!
